## Knowledge References
- `id`: title - used_in - `path`

## Knowledge Outputs
- `id-or-suggested-id`: type - title - action(created/updated/suggested/archived) - `path-or-target`

## Visual Evidence
- reference: `path-or-none`
- screenshot: `path-or-none`
- parity report: `path-or-none`

## Remaining Risks
- ...
```


